*"Ostala* su mu još samo četiri dana do rođendana." (He only had four days left until his birthday.)

*"Ona je *ostala* dugo budna." (She stayed awake for a long time.)

*"Ona je *ostala* veoma iznenađena." (She was very surprised.)

*"On je *ostao* bez posla." (He stayed without job.)

*"Ona se *ostala* dugo sama." (She stayed alone for a long time.)

*"Oni su *ostali* bez voljene osobe." (They stayed without a beloved person.)